channel.title: Congressional Committee Prints - New items on govinfo
channel.description: Provides access to newly published GovInfo content from the Congressional Committee Prints. Congressional Committee Prints are publications issued by Congressional Committees that include topics related to their legislative or research activities, as well as other matters such as memorial tributes.

image.title: Congressional Committee Prints - New items on govinfo

channel.copyright: Title 17, Section 105, United States Code, provides that: Copyright protection under this title is not available for any work of the United States Government, but the United States Government is not precluded from receiving and holding copyrights transferred to it by assignment, bequest, or otherwise. For more information, see https://www.govinfo.gov/about/policies#copyright
